{
  "stem": "26140.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In fact, this was the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Once the last people went in, the SS men and-- were-- they had 60 people working as-- as a special command.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "These were Jewish people, which they picked up from the transport.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They could speak the language of the transport.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they could explain to the people that they-- they going only to be washed and then given work.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Leave all your things quietly down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We'll-- we'll get you out of here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But once they were already full in the chamber, the-- one SS was with the two-- two or three sonderkommando people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They locked the-- the door.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there was a special team of other people who threw the gas, Zyklon-B, through the windows.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And it was instant death.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "After that, they-- they were-- after about half an hour, there was ventilation put on to get the last fragment of the gas out.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the sonderkommando people used to bring them out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They have to have a look whether they had any gold teeth on, to remove them, any valuables around the neck or whatever, rings and so on.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They removed all these.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they also sheared the hair of the women.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I believe they used the hair for the special clothing in the German industry.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The things I saw was the transport being selected and moved in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The rest, I could sometimes see when they-- when I passed, when they were shearing heads off.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I had to move away, because that wasn't the way-- my way to go through.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So main thing I've seen is the selection and sending to the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This area was out of bound.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
